    <string name="instructions_content">【Adding Images】\n• From gallery: tap the \"Add\" button in the pending area and select images.\n• Image packages: open top-right menu → \"Image Packages\" and import a local ZIP (password-protected ZIPs supported).\n• Import target: when importing a package, choose either Pending Images or Character Badges.\n\n【Pending Area】\n• Swipe left/right to browse images.\n• Drag downward to drop an image into a tier.\n• Drag upward out of the area (turns red) to delete.\n• Add/Clear: tap \"Add\" to import from gallery; tap \"Clear\" to remove all pending images.\n\n【Tier Operations】\n• Edit name: tap the tier color block on the left, enter a new name, and confirm.\n• Change color: double-tap the tier color block to pick a preset color or enter a hex value.\n• Delete tier: swipe a tier to the right; release when red to delete.\n• Add tier: tap the \"+\" button at the bottom.\n• Reorder: long-press and drag the tier color block up or down.\n\n【Image Operations in Tier】\n• Tap: open image menu (View / Crop / Move / Replace / Rename / Badges / Narration).\n• Double-tap: select image (blue border); double-tap another to swap positions (across tiers supported).\n• Vertical drag: move images between tiers or back to pending area.\n• Drag upward out of the area (turns red) to delete.\n\n【Image Action Menu】\n• View: view full image and resolution info.\n• Crop: crop to 1:1 or 3:4 ratio, or set a custom pixel size.\n• Move: move image to another tier, or use Front/End/Left/Right to fine-tune position.\n• Replace: choose a new image to replace the current one.\n• Rename: add a name shown below or under the image.\n• Badges: add up to 3 badges; choose built-in or imported badges.\n• Narration Audio: add MP3/WAV/M4A narration for this image.\n\n【Badges】\n• Access: choose \"Badges\" in the image action menu.\n• Limit: up to 3 badges per image.\n• Position: default top-right; enable \"External Badge\" in settings to show on the right side.\n• Source: select from imported badges or import a package to the Character Badges area.\n• Delete: tap the delete button next to a badge to remove it.\n\n【Video Generation】\n• Access: tap the \"Video\" icon in the top toolbar.\n• Action order: adjust the playback order of Place Image / Show Name / Add Badge.\n• Playback order: play per image or per tier.\n• Interval: fixed duration per image, or auto-calculated from associated audio length.\n• Audio overlay: use image narration as background narration; choose to keep or replace action sound effects.\n• Background music: add BGM and set narration/BGM playback order and volume.\n• Preview/Export: preview or export as MP4.\n\n【Preset Management】\nOpen top-right menu → \"Manage Presets\":\n• Save Preset: save current tier list config as a preset.\n• Import Preset: import a .tdds preset file.\n• Export Preset: export current config as a .tdds file to share.\n• Apply/Delete: apply or delete saved presets from the list.\n• Overwrite: choose overwrite or create new when importing an existing preset.\n\n【Draft Auto-Save】\n• Auto-save: app saves current editing state in the background.\n• Restore prompt: asks whether to restore unsaved draft on reopening.\n• Trigger: pressing Home, switching apps, or exiting triggers draft save.\n\n【Other Features】\n• Edit Title: tap the top title to rename the tier list.\n• Edit Author: tap \"By: author\" to change author name.\n• Save: tap bottom \"Save\" to preview and save to gallery.\n• Share: tap \"Share\" in preview to share the image.\n• Reset: tap bottom \"Reset\" to restore default template.\n• Theme toggle: tap sun/moon icon at top to switch light/dark theme.\n• Menu: tap top gear icon for Image Packages, Manage Presets, Settings, Help, Donate, Open Source Licenses.\n• Resource Manager: tap top folder icon to view cache/work directory size and clear cache.\n\n【Settings】\nOpen top-right menu → \"Settings\":\n• Language: switch interface language.\n• System Theme: follow system light/dark mode.\n• Disable Custom Font: use system default font.\n• Disable Tap-to-Add: tapping an image no longer adds it to a tier.\n• External Badge: show badges on the right side of images.\n• Name Below Image: show image names below images.\n• Adjust Float Preview: adjust offset of the floating preview while dragging.</string>

